data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Nestled on a sprawling and meticulously maintained acre, this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is a haven of comfort and entertainment.The living space boasts not one, but two fireplaces, creating a warm and inviting ambiance during those chilly evenings. Generously sized living areas make this an exemplary home for hosting visitors. The dry bar adds a touch of sophistication, making it an ideal spot for crafting cocktails and hosting intimate gatherings. The 7-year-old HVAC unit, along with a brand-new hot water heater installed just 4 months ago, add to the home's efficiency and comfort. Outside, your oasis awaits with a pristine in-ground pool. The pole barn provides ample space for storage.All appliances, expansive camera system, pool accessories and robotic vacuum stay, ensuring a seamless transition for the lucky new owners, Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home - where every day feels like a vacation and hosting becomes joyous!
